+++++ [[span class="overpass"]]THE FOLLOWING INFORMATION IS CONSIDERED HAZARDOUS TO THE PSYCHES AND DEPARTMENTAL OPERATIONS OF DELETIONS PERSONNEL.[[/span]]
@@ @@
+++++ [[span class="overpass"]]INTERNAL COGITATION AUDITORS ARE TO BE INTEGRATED INTO ANY SEMBLANCE SUSPECTED OF UNWANTED THOUGHT PATTERNS.[[/span]]
[[span style="top:3px; right:5px; position:absolute;"]][[size 50%]]//{{preserved via 'ACCUMULUS' backup system}}//[[/size]][[/span]]
[[/div]]
[[=]]
